snippet.title: Longplay of LEGO Harry Potter: Years 5-7
snippet.description:
Longplay of LEGO Harry Potter: Years 5-7, played as the NTSC version on the Nintendo DS. This game's version was released on Nov. 11th, 2011. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

By: Llighty
